metadata.description:
(S O C I A L  M I R R O R S)

A collection of lo-fi inspired images captured over multiple years that have sat isolated and untouched awaiting for their time and place to exist.

B L O S S O M S 
Is a promo for this collection and will be available as an open mint to allow collectors help contribute to the release of this collection and join my genesis collection with a bang..

Image Size: 3008 x 2000  
Location: Glenrothes, Scotland
